<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Deletion Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .notice {
            background-color: #fef3cd;
            border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">{{ app_name }}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Account Deletion Confirmation</h1>
        
        <p>Hello {{ user.firstName }},</p>
        
        <p>We're writing to confirm that your {{ app_name }} account has been successfully deleted as requested.</p>
        
        <div class="notice">
            <strong>Account Summary:</strong><br>
            • Account Email: {{ user.email }}<br>
            • Deletion Date: {{ "now"|date("F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A") }}<br>
            • All associated data has been permanently removed
        </div>
        
        <p>The following data has been permanently deleted:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your user profile and account information</li>
            <li>All designs and projects</li>
            <li>Uploaded media files</li>
            <li>Export history and saved preferences</li>
            <li>Integration settings and credentials</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>We're sorry to see you go and we hope you had a positive experience with {{ app_name }}. If you have any feedback about how we could improve our service, please don't hesitate to reach out to our team.</p>
        
        <p>If you change your mind in the future, you're always welcome to create a new account and rejoin our community.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for being part of the {{ app_name }} community.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{ app_name }} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a system-generated email confirming the deletion of your account. No further action is required.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
